  "texts": [
    "For instance, if the research question requires the use of a touch-screen, can participants still be tracked or are the hands and arms blocking the eye-tracker camera's view of the participant's eyes?",
    "-Connectivity and synchronization.",
    "Can the eye tracker interface with external devices such as electroencephalogram (EEG), galvanic skin response (GSR), or motion capture?",
    "Does it have a transistor-transistor logic (TTL) input or another method to reliably synchronize eyetracking data to data from external devices (cf.",
    "e.g., Xue, Quan, Li, Yue, & Zhang, 2017)?"
  ]
